text: Multidentia castaneae is a species of flowering plants in the family Rubiaceae. It is endemic to Tanzania. == Sources == * Lovett, J. & Clarke, G.P. 1998. Multidentia castaneae. 2006 IUCN Red List of Threatened Species. Downloaded on 22 August 2007.
